#- Local News§0
§0-------------------§0
§0 Tybug says the most§0
§0important form of§0
§0transportation is§0
§0"rails of course!" He§0
§0plans to start building§0
§0a rail to Myten ASAP§0
§0and is determined to§0
§0get the project§0
§0finished. He choose§0
§0Myten because many§0
§0citizens requested
#- it.§0

